                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>2. Technology leads AI adoption</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>The Technology industry demonstrates the highest AI adoption rate, followed by Finance and Manufacturing, reflecting greater digital maturity.</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>3. Education has the lowest AI adoption</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Education remains one of the least AI-enabled industries, suggesting slower digital transformation and untapped opportunities.</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>4. Salary growth continues despite automation</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Average salary growth continues to rise over time, indicating that AI is creating demand for higher-value skills rather than simply reducing wages.</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>5. Job market remains relatively stable</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#b4b4b4' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='3' />
                    <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='10' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                    <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='44066' id='68' type-v2='text' w='43573' x='33977' y='13984'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>👨‍💼 Employee Dashboard Insights</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>1. Reskilling is becoming essential</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>The Analysis highlights the growing need for continuous learning to remain competitive in an AI-driven labor market.</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>2. Customer Support faces the highest automation risk</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Customer Support and Truck Driver roles show the greatest AI replacement potential due to repetitive operational tasks.</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>3. Software Engineers remain highly valued</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Software Engineers continue to receive the highest salaries even after AI adoption,</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>4. Higher education improves job survival</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Employees with PhD and Master&apos;s degrees exhibit the highest job survival scores, suggesting advanced education reduces automation vulnerability.</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>5. AI affects occupations differently</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Technical and analytical jobs experience lower automation risk than repetitive administrative positions.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#b4b4b4' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='3' />
                    <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='10' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                    <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='39953' id='69' type-v2='text' w='77188' x='302' y='58402'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>🌍 Industry Dashboard Insights</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>1. AI adoption continues to increase every year</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>AI adoption demonstrates consistent year-over-year growth, reflecting accelerated digital transformation globally.</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>2. Salary growth follows AI adoption</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>As AI adoption increases, salary growth also rises, suggesting organizations reward AI-related skills.</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>3. Manufacturing shows elevated automation pressure</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Manufacturing experiences high automation intensity, reflecting widespread deployment of robotics and intelligent production systems.</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>4. Finance and Technology remain AI leaders</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Finance and Technology consistently rank among the highest-performing sectors in AI adoption.</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>5. Employment opportunities remain globally balanced</run>
                    <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Despite rising automation, employment remains relatively stable across most countries, suggesting AI is transforming work rather than eliminating it.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#b4b4b4' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='3' />
                    <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='10' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                    <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='24324' id='71' type-v2='text' w='21062' x='78033' y='73561'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>💡 Recommendations</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>1. Invest in continuous employee reskilling and AI literacy programs.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Æ </run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>2.Focus AI implementation on repetitive operational processes first. </run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>3. Encourage higher education and professional certifications to improve workforce resilience.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#b4b4b4' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='3' />
                    <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='10' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                    <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
              </zone>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='8' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
          </zones>
        </devicelayout>
      </devicelayouts>
      <simple-id uuid='{63C54A27-BDFA-4B86-A7AE-5D89D5A141B3}' />
    </dashboard>
